data.description: ***Seller offering a one point buydown.***  Please inquire for more details.  Hollywood Shores welcomes you home!!  This adorable one story rambler not only has water views but access to a community beach and boat ramp, within walking distance. This well maintained home is bright, cheery and inviting.  Upon entering you will find a large foyer, the length of the home.  At the very end you will find a space that can be used as an artist's studio, kids play area or just storage. The home opens up into the large family room with a large kitchen just behind.  Off to the left is a large laundry area with access to the backyard.  And, off to the right you will find a great dining space, with access to the rear entry driveway. The two bedrooms on either side of the full bathroom complete this home.  Your forward facing bedroom has those sought after water views.   And, to complete the home, you'll find a fully fenced backyard.  This gem won't last!  Book your showing today!
